This year=92s theme is =91beyond the book=92, as now, more than ever, peopl=
e are debating what constitutes a book. With the development of ebooks, app=
s, self-publishing and fan fiction =AD=96 as well as the popularity of book=
 adaptations to film, TV, stage and other venues =96 book boundaries are ex=
tended and broken all the time. This conference will consider the many inca=
rnations of stories that take place =91beyond the book=92, as well as the i=
mpact of children=92s books on wider culture, including discussions of the =
publishing industry and book design, digital developments, marginalia, adap=
